{"thag2.23:0.1":"Theragatha 2.23 ","thag2.23:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.23:0.3":"Tatiyavagga ","thag2.23:0.4":"Sobhitattheragatha ","thag2.23:1.1":"“Satima pannava bhikkhu, ","thag2.23:1.2":"araddhabalaviriyo; ","thag2.23:1.3":"Panca kappasatanaham, ","thag2.23:1.4":"ekarattim anussarim. ","thag2.23:2.1":"Cattaro satipatthane, ","thag2.23:2.2":"satta attha ca bhavayam; ","thag2.23:2.3":"Panca kappasatanaham, ","thag2.23:2.4":"ekarattim anussarin”ti. ","thag2.23:2.5":"… Sobhito thero …. "}